summary: This appears to be an email forwarding FBI 302 interview reports related to an individual named Rodgers, likely part of the Epstein investigation. The document references two attached interview reports and indicates communication between FBI personnel and the U.S. Attorney's Office for the Southern District of New York.

events.title: Forwarding of Rodgers 302 reports
events.description: Email communication forwarding FBI 302 interview reports and phone records related to Rodgers between law enforcement officials.

keyFacts: The document references FBI 302 interview reports related to an individual named Rodgers.
The communication involves the U.S. Attorney's Office for the Southern District of New York (USANYS).
Two interview reports are attached to the email: Interview_o.pdf and Interview_ol.pdf.
The email was sent on April 23, 2020, indicating ongoing investigative activity related to the Epstein case.
The document shows coordination between FBI personnel and federal prosecutors in New York.
